T1  - Do exogenous changes in passive institutional ownership affect corporate governance and firm value?
AU  - Schmidt, Cornelius
AU  - Fahlenbrach, Rüdiger
JO  - Journal of Financial Economics
VL  - 124
IS  - 2
SP  - 285
EP  - 306
PY  - 2017
DA  - 2017/05/01/
